Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為是親人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所生活的島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡說八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是通識者軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了攻擊島而利用了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關著你的島被破壞的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還想…利用我做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你帶回你該待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
